info.description: [![](https://codecov.io/gh/nickderobertis/py-ex-latex/branch/master/graph/badge.svg)](https://codecov.io/gh/nickderobertis/py-ex-latex) # py-ex-latex ## Overview This project is aimed at creating LaTeX documents using only Python, without directly writing LaTeX code. Rather than building a direct Python API to LaTeX, this package has its own, simpler API to creating documents. ## Links See the [documentation here.]( https://nickderobertis.github.io/py-ex-latex/ ) ## Author Created by Nick DeRobertis.
